<br>
The names there are pretty tough (i.e. No snares/roots, gate and regen to full health, etc. I would be scared to duo, give me a group of 4 and I'll be happy).  The spawn rate is fairly fast so you have to move fast to get to more than one named.  Also, there are black and gray wolves that wander into the tower to the coterie houses.  Be wary of them.  One reason is because they are a bit tough and do gate (though not as tough as the named).  The other reason is once they get to their final destination after wandering, they supposedly turn into named vampires.<br>
<br>
We did get Spirit of Flame, a level 56 beastlord spell from a named on Sunday so I'm pretty sure that other high level spells will drop.   Maybe I won't see Moonfire from this, but I'll see other spells that I can use and some in my guild could use as well.<br>
<br>
**Edit:  When I say tough, I mean tough for 2-3 people.  Attempting to solo the named could be deadly.  I don't think they summon, but like I said earlier, no snares/roots, gate to regen to full health, high hit points, and they hit kind of hard.** <p><center><img src="http://personal.atl.bellsouth.net/lig/g/r/greenvix/Sig2.jpg"><br><font size=1><a href="http://www.amybrownart.com">Signature Art by Amy Brown</font></a></br></center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukalliasylurian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kallia Sylurian</A> at: 2/5/02 7:09:22 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukotochan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kotochan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(2/7/02 9:49:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2668.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Moonfire / Mask of Stalker</span><hr size=1> Can solo the named vamps easy :P<br>
